    section
        h2 Schedule of Events
        .content
          .text
            p The wedding weekend will begin with an early supper on Friday evening and wrap up with a Halloween brunch on Sunday.      
            h3 Welcome Supper
            i Friday, October 29th
            p Join us for a casual evening at local favorite Comfort Pizza. Meet and greet over wood-fired pies and local beverages. Starting at 5:00pm.
            h3 Wedding and Reception
            i Saturday, October 30th
            p Guests to arrive at the Ingenhuett at 5:00p for a cocktail in the courtyard. Ceremony to start at golden hour--around 5:30p. Dinner, drinks, and dancing to follow. After hours rendezvous at the Meet Market across the street.
